name: Monochrome Battal Ebrû / Marbling Art SE #1
description:
1/1 Special Edition. 
Date created 05 Jan 2021 - High Res image (1512 × 2016 pixels)
Unique piece of hand-made, non-digital marbling art (Ebrû/Turkish Paper).
Created by Ertugrul Incel with traditional Ebrû method, using earth dyes and water-based solution, and transferred on acid-free paper.
